This is Perl module Plack.

INSTALLATION

Plack installation is straightforward. 

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Plack documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Plack

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

